{"tid":2176935,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"G鋒查完車牌之後即刻拉查車牌嘅人","createTime":"2020-08-27T11:15:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-27T17:17:36.000Z","uid":79793,"like":6,"dislike":25,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"eb9de0d87267db3d9bdfdf76a0675676b2356e50","tid":2176935,"uid":79793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T11:15:57.000Z","msg":"【 拘捕 &bull; 涉濫用運輸署系統 &bull; 查取超過1,200人個人資料 】<br />\n<br />\n警方網絡安全及科技罪案調查科人員，昨日（8月26日）於屯門拘捕一名52歲男子，涉嫌自去年六月起，於收取報酬後，進入運輸署網上申請「車輛登記細節證明書」系統，訛稱證明書用作法律訴訟及買賣車輛用途，申請超過1,200份載有不同個人資料（包括姓名、住址、身份證號碼等）的證明書。部分證明書中的個人資料，其後亦被發現在不同的社交媒體平台上不法披露。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hCVzFeE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhCVzFeE.jpg&h=c19b52bc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d11b53b2fb178e61659a4b3778f7c45fd562e6d0","tid":2176935,"uid":81006,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T11:18:10.000Z","msg":"依家仲有得check咁多嘢咩?<br />\n姓名、住址、身份證號碼<br />\n<br />\n我記得之前好似改咗冇咁多嘢可以查到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fcf6463e9cfa45ed142e3ae3b6ff0c55af4a6350","tid":2176935,"uid":335434,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T11:20:04.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.landsearch.com.hk/product/isc/intro.asp?slang=c\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.landsearch.com.hk%2Fproduct%2Fisc%2Fintro.asp%3Fslang%3Dc&d=a8feNXbjtso6d%2BC97Zvpk5X8N1KgQotyuydbLhb69C0%3D&h=9ccbaf3f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.landsearch.com.hk/product/isc/intro.asp?slang=c</a><br />\n原來幫人查冊都唔得 咁拉晒呢啲查冊公司未啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1499338548c65fa9298173c15d3df072a2e11520","tid":2176935,"uid":208314,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T11:20:09.000Z","msg":"所以罪名係...?"},{"pid":"c7029e27342b9565f5af400c835d6d108d55feff","tid":2176935,"uid":79793,"like":2,"dislike":7,"score":-5,"quote":{"pid":"1499338548c65fa9298173c15d3df072a2e11520","tid":2176935,"uid":208314,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T11:20:09.000Z","msg":"所以罪名係...?"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T11:20:55.000Z","msg":"被捕男子涉干犯<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">「披露未經資料使用者同意而取得個人資料」罪</span></span></strong>，一經定罪最高罰款港幣100萬及監禁五年。同時，被捕男子亦可能干犯「為取得道路交通條例下的證明書而作出虛假陳述」罪或「有犯罪或不誠實意圖而取用電腦」罪。此外，警方亦會繼續追緝委託被捕人查取個人資料的人士，不排除稍後有更多人士被捕。<br />\n<br />\n警方提醒市民，高等法院頒布，禁止披露警務人員及其家人個人資料的臨時禁制令仍然生效，大家切勿以身試法。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"313f3fc1a6458c63fe915a4b0dddf64983da22e9","tid":2176935,"uid":20870,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T11:21:39.000Z","msg":"之前有幾單係藍絲群流傳既個人資料拉左咪?"},{"pid":"dfa86882d104ebd00883c2b426389c4bfc99e429","tid":2176935,"uid":199893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T11:25:10.000Z","msg":"On9"},{"pid":"946dfa77242bbd50eb74de51de1f0b64a4833f7a","tid":2176935,"uid":53922,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T11:26:02.000Z","msg":"好嬲好嬲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da47f493e2b4e7576e1e715d54a9ea13dbbb7c45","tid":2176935,"uid":199893,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T11:26:09.000Z","msg":"合法個個人都查到嘅嘢<br />\n律政幾時告埋運輸<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e86478f270330d5556d5432f86c7dba7aea48d5","tid":2176935,"uid":52271,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T11:26:28.000Z","msg":"咁運輸署用呢樣野黎牟利，是咪應該拉人封鋪"},{"pid":"f6c0813371e46c4f06e2dac4b10e4608371318cd","tid":2176935,"u